@startuml sequence-async

skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 30
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam SequenceGroupBodyBackgroundColor #F5F5FF

autonumber
queue "Kafka\nreservation-created" as KafkaReservation
participant "Payment\nService" as Payment
database "payment_db\n(outbox_event)" as PaymentDB
queue "Kafka\npayment-confirmed" as KafkaConfirmed
queue "Kafka\npayment-failed" as KafkaFailed
participant "Notification\nService" as Notification
participant "Reservation\nService" as Reservation

== 3. Payment Processing (async) ==

KafkaReservation -> Payment: Consume ReservationCreatedEvent\n(group: payment-service-group)
activate Payment
Payment -> PaymentDB: BEGIN TRANSACTION\n  1. INSERT payment (status: CREATED)\n  2. INSERT outbox_event (status: NEW)
PaymentDB --> Payment: OK

alt Payment Confirmed (via PATCH /api/payments/{id}/confirm)
    Payment -> PaymentDB: BEGIN TRANSACTION\n  1. UPDATE payment (status: CONFIRMED)\n  2. INSERT outbox_event (PaymentConfirmedEvent)
    Payment -> KafkaConfirmed: Publish PaymentConfirmedEvent\n(Outbox Scheduler)
    activate KafkaConfirmed

    KafkaConfirmed -> Notification: Consume PaymentConfirmedEvent\n(group: notification-service-group)
    activate Notification
    Notification -> Notification: INSERT notification_log
    deactivate Notification

    KafkaConfirmed -> Reservation: Consume PaymentConfirmedEvent\n(group: reservation-service-group)
    activate Reservation
    Reservation -> Reservation: UPDATE reservation\nstatus: PAID
    deactivate Reservation
    deactivate KafkaConfirmed

else Payment Failed (via PATCH /api/payments/{id}/fail)
    Payment -> PaymentDB: BEGIN TRANSACTION\n  1. UPDATE payment (status: FAILED)\n  2. INSERT outbox_event (PaymentFailedEvent)
    Payment -> KafkaFailed: Publish PaymentFailedEvent\n(Outbox Scheduler)
    activate KafkaFailed

    KafkaFailed -> Notification: Consume PaymentFailedEvent\n(group: notification-service-group)
    activate Notification
    Notification -> Notification: INSERT notification_log
    deactivate Notification

    KafkaFailed -> Reservation: Consume PaymentFailedEvent\n(group: reservation-service-group)
    activate Reservation
    Reservation -> Reservation: UPDATE reservation\nstatus: PAYMENT_FAILED
    deactivate Reservation
    deactivate KafkaFailed
end
deactivate Payment

note over KafkaReservation, Reservation
  Full E2E time: 4.7–10.3s (median 5.21s)
  due to 2x Outbox scheduler jitter (0–5s per hop).
  Bimodal distribution caused by fixedDelay=5000ms.
end note

@enduml
